          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21339002-bobo-s-book-bank?shelf=new-adult">new-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21339002-bobo-s-book-bank?shelf=opposites-attract">opposites-attract</a>, 
